column3: When failing to escape a trap, roll a dice. On a 4 to 6, ignore the trap penalty.
When you flip a poison token, roll a dice. On a 4 to 6, ignore the poison penalty.
If another animal steals from you, pay 1 extra coin instead of getting your harvest stolen
Add +4 dexterity when escaping from a hunter
Add +4 dexterity when escaping from the dog
When standing on top of a harvest dice, change it to the fruit/vegetable/hay of your choice.
Change the harvest season token to the harvest type of your choice.
When picking up a harvest, get double the coins.
Get rid of a weak or strong card in your hand. Put it at the bottom of its original deck.
